First Department,

August, 1950.

(August 4, 1950.) In the Matter of Louis A. Mendelsohn, Petitioner, against Bernard G. Walpin, Appellant, and Harry B. Chambers, as Chairman of the Bronx County Committee of the Democratic Party, et al., Respondents.

Appeal transferred to the Second Department of this court for hearing and determination. Present — Glennon, J. P., Dore, Cohn, Callahan and Shientag, JJ.
